(firstQuint)Oxytocin and Emotion Processing.

 An effect of OXT on emotion processing and anxiety has been broadly investigated in animal studies.

 However, in humans, effects seem more complex.

 The rationale of the study is to examine direct effects of OXT to processing and learning of emotional and social values in humans.

